  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Objectives 1.Raise awareness and generate commitment for action to promote gender and women&apos;s rights in Disaster Risk Reduction (DRR) among Oxfam staff and partners and possibly government representatives, through delivery of a series of virtual trainings for Oxfam staff and partners.  2.Raise awareness of women&apos; rights and disaster risk among key stakeholders (national and international NGOs, representatives of agencies of governments and international institutions) through events during the global UNISDR 2012 -13 campaign on gender and DRR and in the processes relevant to the post -2015 Hyogo Framework and  Strategic Development Goals (SDGs).</narrative>
